One little mini tip would be to chain the events, so you don't have to run the selector again:

<code>
$("#search input")
.focus( function() {
if ($(this).val()=="Search") {$(this).val("");}
})
.blur( function() {
if ($(this).val()=="") {$(this).val("Search");}
});
</code>

